# Business Intelligence Tools and Reports Update

1. New Data Visualization Tool
   - Tableau 2023.2 now available
   - Enhanced geospatial analytics capabilities
   - Improved dashboard interactivity features

2. Quarterly Sales Report Enhancements
   - Added year-over-year comparison charts
   - New product category breakdown
   - Interactive filters for region and customer segments

3. Metadata Improvements
   - Updated data dictionary for customer database
   - New tagging system for financial metrics
   - Implemented data lineage tracking for key reports

4. Upcoming BI Training Sessions
   - Introduction to Power BI: June 15th
   - Advanced SQL for Analytics: July 8th
   - Data Storytelling Workshop: July 22nd

5. New Self-Service Analytics Portal
   - Access to pre-built report templates
   - Drag-and-drop report builder
   - Scheduled for launch on August 1st

</OUTPUT_TEXT>
